<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The rowCount() method in the Zend_Db_Statement_Mysqli class assumes that rowCount() should return the number of rows in a result set.  This method is intended to also return the number of rows affected by an INSERT, UPDATE, or DELETE statement.</p>

<p>Please use mysqli_affected_rows() instead of the metadata row_num from the result set of a SELECT.</p>

